{"title":"美食节介绍","icon":"dining","desc":"部分图片来自东北师范大学官网与东北师范大学官方微信公众号","shareable":true,"id":"newcomer/intro/activity/festival","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"info","text":["学校每年定期举办美食节，这是一项集美食评选与文化展示于一体的校园品牌活动。","活动期间，各食堂档口将精心制作招牌菜品参与评比，评选结束后，部分菜品会向师生提供免费品尝。此外，美食节当天，所有食堂档口均提供折扣优惠（例如全场八折）。"]},{"tag":"card","cover":"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/s67UCDghNJnvrnSHL17d4licOamoQt8OpgakUvGmcsiaWfgWBW8YxXtGRnUpyaVVEiayWOwDKkqVLRkeCg2nSmqjQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg","url":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/HTWlygZatf5KQLykmgko9w","title":"东北师范大学第七届美食节","logo":"$img/organization/nenuyouth.png","name":"东师青年"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/benbu-festival1.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/benbu-festival2.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/benbu-festival3.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/benbu-festival4.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/jingyue-festival1.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/jingyue-festival2.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/jingyue-festival3.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/jingyue-festival4.jpg"},{"tag":"title","text":"北苑"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival1.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival2.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival3.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival4.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival5.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival6.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival7.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival8.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/beiyuan/festival9.jpg"},{"tag":"title","text":"南苑"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/nanyuan/festival1.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/nanyuan/festival2.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/nanyuan/festival3.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/nanyuan/festival4.jpg"},{"tag":"title","text":"一食堂"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/dining1/festival1.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/dining/dining1/festival2.jpg"},{"tag":"p","type":"tip","header":"Mr.Hope の 吐槽","text":["与其说是美食节，不如戏称为“萝卜雕刻大赛”。味道好坏似乎是次要的，关键在于菜品摆盘的观赏性。为了在评比中脱颖而出，各个档口都会卯足了劲，用萝卜等食材雕刻出精美的造型作为装饰。","活动的另一大亮点是学校会提供一个超大尺寸的免费蛋糕，分发给前来参加的同学。同时，参与评比的档口也会在展示结束后，将部分美食免费提供给师生品尝。","不过，对于大一、大二的同学来说，想品尝到免费美食颇具挑战。因为课程安排，等你下课赶到食堂时，免费的菜品和蛋糕往往已经被“一扫而空”了。"]}],"time":"2025 年 7 月 23 日 09:43:28"}